{"tid":575330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【預算案迴響】林鄭讚揚秉承理財新哲學　張建宗：帶來希望歡欣","createTime":"2018-02-28T06:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T08:49:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f02167a6778dadfa1b9e67f5e8c7952cee4565","tid":575330,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180228/s00001/8d7c3455dd6a14a48556c32e07f86c85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180228%2Fs00001%2F8d7c3455dd6a14a48556c32e07f86c85.jpg&h=cbb00c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新一份《財政預算案》公布後，行政長官林鄭月娥發聲明，讚揚《預算案》秉承本屆政府確立的管治新風格、政府新角色和理財新哲學，又感謝財政司長陳茂波為教育額外預留每年20億元，讓她在競選政綱中承諾的教育新資源，增至70億元，而政府會為如何運用新資源訂定優次。<br />\n<br />\n政務司長張建宗指，《預算案》配合在年中成立、由他擔任主席的三個委員會，包括兒童事務委員會、 青年發展委員會以及人力資源規劃委員會。其中人力資源規劃委員會的工作，製定人才清單的工作已進入最後階段，預料今年年中完成。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，《預算案》為本港帶來希望、歡欣及動力，促請立法會盡快通過撥款條例草案，讓一系列利民措盡快落實，推動香港向前邁進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180228/s00001/1519796231343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180228%2Fs00001%2F1519796231343&d=8E%2FQ2uQKdDQCTUD1LlaSYtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=788397c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180228%2Fs00001%2F1519796231343&h=7b480f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180228/s00001/1519796231343</a>"},{"pid":"3366c9eb27c29c7c4bf04c4353771b4c9a1db0e6","tid":575330,"uid":4525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:36:02.000Z","msg":"做到野，有op去<br />\n拎埋兩千跟波子哥哥淘寶"},{"pid":"2e62f23958239816cdf41fe519b8f340215ef6c7","tid":575330,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"啲錢用晒但好似無做過嘢咁,高招"},{"pid":"e7ffb9e6c0f120bc6de7d57d669a0ebf7d24cdc1","tid":575330,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"中學雞唱好政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e96f1a8c3fa2de1a6913939e990f8c8f4eb087","tid":575330,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"a2ae6ecaa8a3d2a6183335cc150d8a521b39be68","tid":575330,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"好心喇 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d966098c5218e737cd835d0175138924b13eb4d3","tid":575330,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a0bdcef2783dbc13172dbd8ea03fcd3b6385968","tid":575330,"uid":59901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:31:27.000Z","msg":"我做埋個司長仲歡欣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3014e17b55d4e7f0d791d3fc56c93ff57c1b85b3","tid":575330,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"張建宗慳到幾多差餉？"}]}